high_descs: Turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the dirty mug that's at the coffee maker.
Turn around and walk to the sink then turn left to face it.
Wash the mug in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Walk back over to the coffee maker.
Put the mug back where you got it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go face the coffee machine.
Pick up the white mug that's in the coffee machine.
Go back to your right with the mug and face the sink.
Put the mug in the sink to wash it, then grab it up again.
Bring the mug back over to the coffee machine.
Put it back down where you found it in the machine.
anns.task_desc: Wash the coffee mug and put it back.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker.
Turn right to face the sink.
Wash the cup in the sink and remove it.
Turn left and step forward to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To wash a cup as well as place it back in the coffee maker.
